<module>
    <h>sgoil</h>
    <p><g>sgoil</g>
        <fem/>
        <en>a school</en></p>

    <section>
        <h>adjectives</h>
        <module id="moor">
            <h>mór</h>
            <p><g>sgoil <a href="?gd=moor">mhór</a></g>
                <en>a big school</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil an sgoil mór? Tha.</gd>
                        <tr>Is the school big? Yes, it is.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl></p>
        </module>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>nouns</h>
        <section>
            <h>people</h>
            <module id="caileag">
                <h>caileag</h>
                <p><g><a href="?gd=caileag">caileag</a> ann an sgoil</g>
                    <en>a girl in a school</en> – <xl>
                        <li>
                            <gd>Cha robh a’ chaileag bheag anns an sgoil.</gd>
                            <tr>The little girl was not in the school.</tr>
                            <ref text="617">td. 15 [228]</ref>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <gd>An do ruith a’ chaileag do’n sgoil? Ruith.</gd>
                            <tr>Did the girl run to the school?</tr>
                            <ref text="617">td. 47</ref>
                        </li>
                    </xl>
                </p>
            </module>
            <section id="other">
                <h>other</h>
                <p><xl>
                        <li>
                            <gd>A bheil Seònaid anns an sgoil an diugh? Chan eil.</gd>
                            <tr>Is Janet in the school today? No, she isn’t.</tr>
                            <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                        </li>
                    </xl>
                </p>
            </section>
        </section>
        <module id="leabhar">
            <h>leabhar</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=leabhar">leabhar</a> ann an sgoil</g>
                <en>a book in a school</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Dh’fhàg mi mo leabhar anns an sgoil.</gd>
                        <tr>I left my book in the school.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 47</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An do dh’fhàg thu do leabhar anns an sgoil? Cha do dh’fhàg. Càit an do
                            dh’fhàg thu do leabhar? Dh’fhàg mi mo leabhar air a bhòrd.</gd>
                        <tr>Did you leave your book in the school? No, I didn’t. Where did you leave
                            your book? I left my book on the table.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 48</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>verbs</h>
        <module id="rach">
            <h>rach</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=rach">rach</a> ... do sgoil</g>
                <en>... goes to a school</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An do dh’fhan Màiri aig an taigh an diugh? Cha do dh’fhan. Chaidh Màiri
                            do’n sgoil anns a’ mhadainn</gd>
                        <tr>Did Mary stay at home today? No, she didn’t. She went to school in the
                            morning.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 237–8</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Dh’éirich Màiri agus Calum tràth anns a’ mhadainn an diugh, oir bha iad
                            ri dhol do’n sgoil.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary and Malcolm rose early in the morning today, for they had to go to
                            the school.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 182–3</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
        <module id="faag">
            <h>fàg</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=faag">fàg</a> ... ann an sgoil ...</g>
                <en>... leaves ... in a school</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Dh’fhàg mi mo leabhar anns an sgoil.</gd>
                        <tr>I left my book in the school.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 47</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An do dh’fhàg thu do leabhar anns an sgoil? Cha do dh’fhàg. Càit an do
                            dh’fhàg thu do leabhar? Dh’fhàg mi mo leabhar air a bhòrd.</gd>
                        <tr>Did you leave your book in the school? No, I didn’t. Where did you leave
                            your book? I left my book on the table.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 48</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
        <module id="ruith">
            <h>ruith</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=ruith">ruith</a> ... do sgoil</g>
                <en>... runs to a school</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>An do ruith a’ chaileag do’n sgoil? Ruith.</gd>
                        <tr>Did the girl run to the school?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 47</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
    </section>



